snippet: Roger Federer and Serena Williams have pulled out of the International Premier Tennis League ahead of the tournament's Indian leg next week due to economic "uncertainty", organizers said on Tuesday....
lead_paragraph: Roger Federer and Serena Williams have pulled out of the International Premier Tennis League ahead of the tournament's Indian leg next week due to economic "uncertainty", organizers said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Federer, Serena Out of International Premier Tennis League
